**Summary:**  
CXL’s AEO guide is comprehensive and well-structured but lacks implementation-focused guidance, detailed tool and tracking recommendations, organizational strategy insights, and deeper multi-engine and content quality nuances that competitors consistently feature. Addressing these critical and opportunity gaps will better equip CXL to lead in the AEO content space with actionable, strategic, and practical content.